{"tid":1657168,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國在湄公河建大壩 當地居民嘆：神被殺了","createTime":"2019-10-16T03:16:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T03:52:54.000Z","uid":75656,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"503e4dfa83a8855b9a6ca85b7b94a18d43fb5141","tid":1657168,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T03:16:50.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國在許多國家推動基礎建設，造成當地生態與債務問題，外媒報導中國在湄公河建造大壩對當地影響，有柬埔寨的當地居民感嘆，這條河就像一個神，「我們把它殺了，這讓我很難過」。<br />\n<br />\n《紐約時報中文網》報導，今年中國在寮國建成大壩，當地村落遭到拆除，中國水利水電建設集團在遠處蓋給居民簡陋竹屋做為補償，當地不識字的居民感到相當無奈。報導指出，21世紀初湄公河委員會預測，蓋大壩可以讓寮國、泰國、柬埔寨和越南得到300億美元的好處，但多年後評估，若真的進行這些項目，下游國家將遭受70億美元的損失。<br />\n<br />\n報導表示，去年中國一家公司就寮國大型水壩項目發布報告，被發現抄襲先前另一個項目的環評報告，專家感嘆，依賴湄公河的人，對這條河的命運支配權卻最小，也有人質疑，這些大壩是為了湄公河下游國家的利益，還是像中國這樣想要獲得經濟影響力、轉嫁過剩產能國家的利益。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，在南烏江梯級電站工地，基本上沒有寮國工人，有碎石廠的中國主管認為，被迫搬遷的居民僅獲得微少補償「不值一提」，因為「不吃苦中苦，難得甜中甜」。報導文末說，湄公河是下游國家的生命線，柬埔寨西公村的居民也因為建造大壩而被遷出，失去了維繫幾代人生活的河流，當地人感嘆地說，這條河就像一個神，「我們把它殺了，這讓我很難過」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2946749\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2946749&d=TC1Ad7l9MtPLjBCdpR1LViWBhM8hN5wqk8YifI4Fu34%3D&h=8b8402fa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2946749&h=d82961e5\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2946749</a>"},{"pid":"fa73281220c07e9282ba18ca4fbe479d532c4994","tid":1657168,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T03:17:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bHH8FUF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbHH8FUF.jpg&h=3fd66e79&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"2440feabe2f115203c5ee8f1869273490176c7d8","tid":1657168,"uid":40267,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T03:19:35.000Z","msg":"奶共呀嗱<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n陸續有嚟呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5214580d3aa3235c8bdabcba0df15823ceb831b4","tid":1657168,"uid":327462,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T03:21:23.000Z","msg":"乜支那有拜神既自由架咩 番去拜維屁神啦支那豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61ff4a9f44a46cb44da4d0a8ceec9d72a7b16392","tid":1657168,"uid":327462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5214580d3aa3235c8bdabcba0df15823ceb831b4","tid":1657168,"uid":327462,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T03:21:23.000Z","msg":"乜支那有拜神既自由架咩 番去拜維屁神啦支那豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T03:21:39.000Z","msg":"維尼神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be85183375bb0449dec2cfe45eca17ccd155c85d","tid":1657168,"uid":121146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T03:23:35.000Z","msg":"有維尼  仲需要湄公河神？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aea79dbbbd08452b469f6d7d6469c0acd50e0b4c","tid":1657168,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T03:24:29.000Z","msg":"觀音像都炸啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />神被殺好正常"},{"pid":"088378681bb1939bb8ddd49437d7488b35cf634a","tid":1657168,"uid":2994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T03:25:15.000Z","msg":"愛國日常<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f610853665db19a13071fd0cd3711704e3ec6c1","tid":1657168,"uid":286155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T03:28:49.000Z","msg":"大淫婦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd5d45fb1d3d3fd54a97371a50bf7c52d7d9ce62","tid":1657168,"uid":268537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T03:30:10.000Z","msg":"一帶一路仲有水魚上釣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkg